Bi thc hnh chng 2 (phn 2): 26 - CANNY EDGE DETECTOR

I> L thuyt

1. Tm hiu v cc bc ca thut ton Canny

a - Gii thch chi tit tng bc:

Thut ton pht hin cnh Canny l mt phng php ph bin bao gm cc bc sau:

  1. Gim nhiu (Noise Reduction): V pht hin cnh rt nhy cm vi nhiu, bc u tin l lc nhiu trong nh bng b lc Gaussian (Gaussian filter). iu ny gip lm mt nh v ngn chn cc cnh gi do nhiu gy ra.
  2. Tnh ton Gradient (Finding Intensity Gradients): nh lm mt sau c lc bng ht nhn Sobel theo c chiu ngang v chiu dc ly o hm bc nht ($G_x$ v $G_y$). T , ln cnh (Edge Gradient) v hng (Direction) cho mi pixel c tnh ton:
    • $Edge\_Gradient (G) = \sqrt{G_x^2 + G_y^2}$
    • $Angle (\theta) = \tan^{-1}(\frac{G_y}{G_x})$ Gc dc c lm trn n mt trong bn gc i din: 0, 45, 90 hoc 135 .
  3. Non-maximum Suppression (Trit tiu phi cc i): Bc ny loi b cc pixel khng phi l cc i cc b theo hng gradient. Thut ton s qut qua ton b nh, ti mi pixel, n kim tra xem liu pixel c phi l cc i cc b trong vng ln cn ca n theo hng gradient hay khng. Nu khng, n s b t v 0 (loi b).
  4. Ngng kp (Hysteresis Thresholding): Bc ny quyt nh pixel no thc s l cnh. Cn hai gi tr ngng: minVal v maxVal.
    • Cnh mnh: Cc pixel c gradient ln hn maxVal chc chn l cnh.
    • Cnh yu: Cc pixel c gradient nm gia minVal v maxVal c coi l cnh yu (tim nng).
    • Khng phi cnh: Cc pixel c gradient nh hn minVal b loi b.
  5. Theo di cnh (Edge Tracking by Hysteresis): Cc cnh yu c gi li ch khi chng kt ni vi cc cnh mnh. iu ny da trn gi nh rng cc cnh nhiu hoc bin i mu nh s khng kt ni vi cc ng vin mnh.

b - So snh vi cc thut ton khc nh Sobel, Laplacian:

c im Canny Sobel Laplacian
Nguyn l Da trn ti u ha a bc (Gradient + NMS + Thresholding). Da trn o hm bc nht (Gradient). Da trn o hm bc hai (Zero-crossing).
chnh xc Cao, pht hin cnh mnh (1 pixel), nh v tt. Trung binh, cnh thng dy v th. Nhy cm vi nhiu cao, c th to cnh kp.
Nhiu X l nhiu tt nh Gaussian filter tch hp. Nhy cm vi nhiu. Rt nhy cm vi nhiu.
phc tp Cao hn (nhiu bc tnh ton). Thp, tnh ton nhanh. Thp.

2. Cc tham s ca thut ton v nh hng ca chng

a - Sigma trong Gaussian filter:

  • Tham s ny xc nh mc lm mt ca nh.
  • Sigma ln: Lm mt nhiu hn, loi b nhiu tt hn nhng cng lm m cc cnh chi tit, c th lm mt cc cnh yu.
  • Sigma nh: Lm mt t hn, gi li nhiu chi tit hn nhng cng gi li nhiu nhiu hn.

b - Ngng thp (minVal) v ngng cao (maxVal):

  • Quyt nh nhy ca vic pht hin cnh.
  • Khong cch gia hai ngng ln: t cnh nhiu hn nhng c th lm t on cc cnh.
  • Ngng thp qu nh: S bt c nhiu nhiu l cnh.
  • Ngng cao qu ln: C th b st cc cnh m.
  • T l thng dng l 1:2 hoc 1:3.

3. u im v nhc im ca Canny edge detector. Cc ng dng thc t

u im:

  • Kh nng pht hin li thp (Low error rate).
  • nh v im cnh tt (Good localization).
  • Phn hi duy nht cho mt cnh (Single edge response).

Nhc im:

  • Phc tp v mt tnh ton so vi Sobel/Prewitt.
  • Kh iu chnh tham s ngng t ng cho mi loi nh.

Cc ng dng thc t:

a - So snh v hiu sut:

  • Canny thng chm hn Sobel do nhiu bc x l, nhng cho kt qu chnh xc hn nhiu cho cc tc v cn tin cy cao.

b - Lnh vc ph bin:

  • Th gic my tnh (Computer Vision): Nhn dng i tng, trch xut c trng.
  • Y t: Phn tch nh X-quang, MRI tm bin khi u, c quan.
  • Cng nghip: Kim tra sn phm, pht hin li vt nt.
  • Xe t li: Pht hin ln ng.

c - V d c th:

  • Pht hin bin bo giao thng.
  • Nhn dng vn tay.
  • Scan ti liu (xc nh bin giy).

    print(f"Warning: Image not found at {image_path}. Please check the path.")
else:
    # c nh bng OpenCV
    img_cv = cv2.imread(image_path, cv2.IMREAD_GRAYSCALE)
    
    # c nh  dng vi Scikit-image (c dng mu ri chuyn xm)
    img_ski = io.imread(image_path)

    plt.figure(figsize=(10, 5))

    plt.imshow(img_cv, cmap='gray')

    plt.axis('off')
    plt.show()

2. Thay i cc tham s v quan st kt qu

a) Thay i Sigma (Scikit-image)

In[5]:
sigmas = [0.1, 1.0, 3.0]
plt.figure(figsize=(15, 5))

for i, sig in enumerate(sigmas):
    edges = feature.canny(img_ski_gray, sigma=sig)
    plt.subplot(1, 3, i + 1)
    plt.imshow(edges, cmap='gray')
    plt.title(f'Sigma = {sig}')
    plt.axis('off')
plt.show()

Nhn xt: Sigma cng ln, nh cng c lm mt nhiu hn trc khi pht hin cnh, dn n t chi tit hn (ch cc cnh rt mnh mi c gi li).

b) Thay i Ngng (OpenCV)

3. p dng Canny cho cc loi nh khc nhau

Chng ta s gi lp cc iu kin nh khc nhau t nh gc kim tra: nh nhiu, nh tng phn thp.

In[7]:
from skimage.util import random_noise
from skimage import exposure

# 1. nh nhiu (Salt & Pepper)
noisy_img = random_noise(img_ski_gray, mode='s&p', amount=0.05)
noisy_img_uint8 = (noisy_img * 255).astype(np.uint8)

# 2. nh  tng phn thp
low_contrast_img = exposure.rescale_intensity(img_ski_gray, in_range=(0.3, 0.7))
low_contrast_img_uint8 = (low_contrast_img * 255).astype(np.uint8)

# p dng Canny
edges_noisy = cv2.Canny(noisy_img_uint8, 100, 200)
edges_low_contrast = cv2.Canny(low_contrast_img_uint8, 50, 150) # Cn gim ngng cho nh tng phn thp

plt.figure(figsize=(12, 10))

plt.subplot(2, 2, 1); plt.imshow(noisy_img, cmap='gray'); plt.title('Noisy Image')
plt.subplot(2, 2, 2); plt.imshow(edges_noisy, cmap='gray'); plt.title('Canny on Noisy Image')

plt.subplot(2, 2, 3); plt.imshow(low_contrast_img, cmap='gray'); plt.title('Low Contrast Image')
plt.subplot(2, 2, 4); plt.imshow(edges_low_contrast, cmap='gray'); plt.title('Canny on Low Contrast')

plt.show()

nh gi:

  • Vi nh nhiu, Canny d bt nhm nhiu thnh cnh nu khng tng sigma (lm mt) hoc tng ngng.
  • Vi nh tng phn thp, gradients nh nn cn gim ngng pht hin c cnh, nhng cng d b nhiu hn.

contours, _ = cv2.findContours(edges_cv, cv2.RETR_EXTERNAL, cv2.CHAIN_APPROX_SIMPLE)

III> Cc cu hi m rng

1. Lm th no nh gi cht lng ca cc cnh c pht hin bi Canny?

  • nh lng: S dng cc s liu nh Precision, Recall, F-measure so vi Ground Truth (nh bin chun do con ngi gn nhn). S dng thang o nh FOM (Figure of Merit) ca Pratt.
  • nh tnh: Kim tra kh nng kt ni (continuity) ca cc cnh, mnh (thinness) ca cnh (l tng l 1 pixel), v kh nng loi b nhiu.

2. C nhng phng php no khc ci thin hiu sut ca Canny?

  • T ng xc nh ngng (Otsu's method): Thay v chn ngng th cng, dng thng k ca nh chn ngng min v max ng.
  • Adaptive Canny: p dng cc tham s khc nhau cho tng vng ca nh da trn c tnh cc b.
  • Tin x l tt hn: S dng Bilateral Filter thay v Gaussian gi bin tt hn trong khi lc nhiu.

3. Canny c th c s dng pht hin cc cnh trong nh mu khng? Nu c, th nh th no?

  • C. Thng thng ngi ta chuyn nh mu sang xm (Grayscale) trc khi p dng Canny.
  • Tuy nhin, c th p dng Canny trn tng knh mu (R, G, B) ring bit v sau gp kt qu li (dng php OR logic hoc ly max gradient) tng chnh xc nhng ni c s thay i mu sc nhng sng khng i.

4. Lm th no p dng Canny cho cc video?

  • Video l chui cc khung hnh (frames). Ta p dng thut ton Canny cho tng frame ring l.
  • n nh kt qu gia cc frame (trnh cnh nhp nhy), c th s dng thng tin t frame trc lm mt hoc iu chnh ngng ng.
